options.text: 遰 What's wrong?
Can you make me a cake?
You don't look very happy.
Nice hat!

3e050b69-6512-40b6-91eb-186eced5f88c.title: Cook
3e050b69-6512-40b6-91eb-186eced5f88c.text:
Oh, dear, oh dear, oh dear. I'm in a terrible
mess! It's the Duke's birthday today, and I should be
making him a lovely big birthday cake.

b06c8d19-328e-44fd-ad83-3d4a50709f0f.title: Cook
b06c8d19-328e-44fd-ad83-3d4a50709f0f.text:
I've forgotten to buy the ingredients. I'll never get
them in time now. He'll sack me! What will I do? I have
four children and a goat to look after. Would you help
me? Please?

options.text: 遰 I'm always happy to help a cook in distress.
I can't right now, Maybe later.

d5dd88d0-d34c-40b3-a2e3-bbfef1714d0a.title: Cook
d5dd88d0-d34c-40b3-a2e3-bbfef1714d0a.text:
Oh thank you, thank you. I need milk, an egg and
flour. I'd be very grateful if you can get them for me.

756c273a-52ab-430d-9bad-7b724ac7769c.title: <player>
756c273a-52ab-430d-9bad-7b724ac7769c.text: So where do I find these ingredients then?

options.text: Where do I find some flour?
How about milk?
And eggs? Where are they found?
Actually, I know where to find this stuff.

92b1339a-f701-42f2-9d65-f1a324227b40.title: Cook
92b1339a-f701-42f2-9d65-f1a324227b40.text:
There is a Mill fairly close, go North and then West.
Mill Lane Mill is just off the road to Draynor. I
usually get my flour from there.

9392c3ae-490f-4d6b-ad29-f38e73ad639a.title: Cook
9392c3ae-490f-4d6b-ad29-f38e73ad639a.text:
Talk to Millie, she'll help, she's a lovely girl and a fine
Miller..

de01eaab-eb1d-42c8-bdef-470cef923ddb.title: Cook
de01eaab-eb1d-42c8-bdef-470cef923ddb.text:
There is a cattle field on the other side of the river,
just across the road from Groats' Farm.

24f1a2f5-8042-41bb-a926-beb51c7c34bf.title: Cook
24f1a2f5-8042-41bb-a926-beb51c7c34bf.text:
Talk to Gillie Groats, she look after the Dairy Cows -
she'll tell you everything you need to know about
milking cows!

dc04df1a-60b7-4d12-9ad8-d1f91548dcc3.title: Cook
dc04df1a-60b7-4d12-9ad8-d1f91548dcc3.text:
I normally get my eggs from the Groats' farm, on the
other side of the river.

e88a7964-5971-45d8-8135-73c1bd845758.title: Cook
e88a7964-5971-45d8-8135-73c1bd845758.text: But any chicken should lay eggs.

ae9b2e90-77bb-40da-9294-f7a0e39cdd89.title: <player>
ae9b2e90-77bb-40da-9294-f7a0e39cdd89.text: I've got all the information I need. Thanks.

1aac62ea-ac0d-4541-ac8c-ad5dac1558b1.title: <player>
1aac62ea-ac0d-4541-ac8c-ad5dac1558b1.text: No, I don't feel like it. Maybe later.

e6e4d17c-112c-4718-86bc-ac2d05965aef.title: Cook
e6e4d17c-112c-4718-86bc-ac2d05965aef.text:
Fine. I always knew you Adventurer types were callous
beasts. Go on your merry way!

b6be8f54-f794-48a4-8b87-a762f5f661fa.title: <player>
b6be8f54-f794-48a4-8b87-a762f5f661fa.text: You're a cook, why don't you bake me a cake?

cdd9fdbe-c244-401e-b000-eaf1f562ea5c.title: Cook
cdd9fdbe-c244-401e-b000-eaf1f562ea5c.text: *sniff* Don't talk to me about cakes...

c26155dc-ee76-4466-b021-c905cd705f4a.title: Cook
c26155dc-ee76-4466-b021-c905cd705f4a.text:
No, I'm not. The world is caving in around me - I am
overcome by dark feelings of impending down.

options.text: What's wrong?
I'd take the rest of the day off if I were you.

1d733197-0bcf-430a-bd2d-126adf1a3f79.title: <player>
1d733197-0bcf-430a-bd2d-126adf1a3f79.text: I'd take the rest of the day off if I were you.

ba3aa6ed-325e-40f0-8ec8-22dca76fa1a1.title: Cook
ba3aa6ed-325e-40f0-8ec8-22dca76fa1a1.text:
No, that's the worst thing I could do. I'd get in terrible
trouble.

39eb0185-3ece-41b4-a4f4-661d24131cdf.title: <player>
39eb0185-3ece-41b4-a4f4-661d24131cdf.text: Well, maybe you need to take a holiday...

64443a7e-4508-44ff-9626-8041228e4b02.title: Cook
64443a7e-4508-44ff-9626-8041228e4b02.text:
That would be nice, but the Duke doesn't allow holidays
for core staff.

798fb601-5ba6-4bf3-96aa-3051157fa0d6.title: <player>
798fb601-5ba6-4bf3-96aa-3051157fa0d6.text:
Hmm, why not run away to the sea and start a new
 life as a Pirate?

e349a311-63ee-418a-9e11-08a243694dac.title: Cook
e349a311-63ee-418a-9e11-08a243694dac.text:
My wife gets sea sick, and I have an irrational fear of
eyepatches. I don't see it working myself.

cb87f1db-b549-48cf-acf1-93a7483af94a.title: <player>
cb87f1db-b549-48cf-acf1-93a7483af94a.text: I'm afraid I've run out of ideas.

810f5344-ec1c-4b65-9548-f6926cb73f34.title: Cook
810f5344-ec1c-4b65-9548-f6926cb73f34.text: Err thank you. It's a pretty ordinary cooks hat really.

dc72f0ac-4c84-4a56-8671-2d85d7eeeb11.title: <player>
dc72f0ac-4c84-4a56-8671-2d85d7eeeb11.text: Still suits you. The trousers are pretty special too.

908808b7-0865-487d-b5e0-c85e92329002.title: Cook
908808b7-0865-487d-b5e0-c85e92329002.text: It's all standard cook's issue uniform...

05d66e3b-680d-4d26-afc4-14325eb3cbb8.title: <player>
05d66e3b-680d-4d26-afc4-14325eb3cbb8.text:
The whole hat, apron, stripey trousers ensemble - it
works. It make you look like a real cook.

29dcab99-e60c-4023-a287-27e5dffda8d2.title: Cook
29dcab99-e60c-4023-a287-27e5dffda8d2.text:
I am a real cook! I haven't got time to be chatting
about culinary fashion. I am in desperate need of help!

7c64989f-7ac8-49fa-8920-dab85418dddd.title: Cook
7c64989f-7ac8-49fa-8920-dab85418dddd.text:
You've brought me everything I need! I am saved!
Thank you!

e1dff6fa-d474-41fa-8a24-eaf2d00f49b0.title: <player>
e1dff6fa-d474-41fa-8a24-eaf2d00f49b0.text: So do I get to go to the Duke's Party?

07d2bbd4-34d8-49eb-9755-ef9e4f048893.title: Cook
07d2bbd4-34d8-49eb-9755-ef9e4f048893.text:
I'm afraid not, only the big cheeses get to dine with the
Duke.

2c8f3a58-b363-4059-bf32-27c10cd76708.title: <player>
2c8f3a58-b363-4059-bf32-27c10cd76708.text:
Well, maybe one day I'll be important enough to sit on
the Duke's table.

6018236a-2de6-47ee-8954-5a40b9741a5e.title: Cook
6018236a-2de6-47ee-8954-5a40b9741a5e.text: Maybe, but I won't be holding my breath.

31392e0a-e22d-46f9-b534-48b7637a349a.title: Cook
31392e0a-e22d-46f9-b534-48b7637a349a.text: How are you getting on with finding the ingredients?

3e38835e-4cdc-46e9-bb13-5307590bbe94.title: <player>
3e38835e-4cdc-46e9-bb13-5307590bbe94.text: I haven't got all of them yet, I'm still looking.

859409c3-1c59-4c81-910c-d7384bb2ad8b.title: Cook
859409c3-1c59-4c81-910c-d7384bb2ad8b.text:
Please get the ingredients quickly. I'm running out of
time! The Duke will throw me into the streets!

options.text: I'll get right on it.
Can you remind me how to find these things again?

9799062a-4580-41bf-b32d-06dde6e0e92d.title: <player>
9799062a-4580-41bf-b32d-06dde6e0e92d.text: Can you remind me how to find these things again?

options.text: Where do I find some flour?
How about milk?
And eggs? Where are they found?
Actually, I know where to find this stuff.

9129cc48-6c1e-41a1-b7c5-8987c76c85b3.title: Cook
9129cc48-6c1e-41a1-b7c5-8987c76c85b3.text:
There is a Mill fairly close, go North and then West.
Mill Lane Mill is just off the road to Draynor. I
usually get my flour from there.

6b369098-0212-4445-8324-0c544df2c776.title: Cook
6b369098-0212-4445-8324-0c544df2c776.text:
Talk to Millie, she'll help, she's a lovely girl and a fine
Miller..

e2da968a-2ebb-449e-bae6-0b7eaf98fd06.title: Cook
e2da968a-2ebb-449e-bae6-0b7eaf98fd06.text:
There is a cattle field on the other side of the river,
just across the road from Groats' Farm.

c195ecc0-5c18-47e2-b8a7-041a87c21e13.title: Cook
c195ecc0-5c18-47e2-b8a7-041a87c21e13.text:
Talk to Gillie Groats, she look after the Dairy Cows -
she'll tell you everything you need to know about
milking cows!

25f89300-251b-4782-a060-03343575d322.title: Cook
25f89300-251b-4782-a060-03343575d322.text:
I normally get my eggs from the Groats' farm, on the
other side of the river.

a467853c-2929-4cd4-8578-e50ce8415f50.title: Cook
a467853c-2929-4cd4-8578-e50ce8415f50.text: But any chicken should lay eggs.

ccbcd1a4-1ac6-4bc8-930e-92f451d47d9b.title: <player>
ccbcd1a4-1ac6-4bc8-930e-92f451d47d9b.text: I've got all the information I need. Thanks.

a478deef-fb52-4133-a879-5f3ed37db806.title: Cook
a478deef-fb52-4133-a879-5f3ed37db806.text: Hello friend, how is the adventuring going?

options.text: I am getting strong and mighty.
I keep on dying.
Can I use your range?

396548a5-29d0-4b55-9b82-b3d6dff20349.title: <player>
396548a5-29d0-4b55-9b82-b3d6dff20349.text: I am getting strong and mighty. Grrr

49d97496-a88e-4fb2-aa10-41ff1099394f.title: Cook
49d97496-a88e-4fb2-aa10-41ff1099394f.text: Ah well, at least you keep coming back to life!

115558c6-414e-41bd-81be-1ec178a71196.title: Cook
115558c6-414e-41bd-81be-1ec178a71196.text:
Go ahead - it's a very good range. It's easier to use
than most other ranges.

4b9ccd05-da5f-4d40-8c8c-f9fee7dd0628.title: Cook
4b9ccd05-da5f-4d40-8c8c-f9fee7dd0628.text:
Its called the Cook-o-matic 100. It uses a combination of
state of the art temperature regulation and magic.

ee7e44fc-2bf5-4fd7-a376-01183711a4a0.title: <player>
ee7e44fc-2bf5-4fd7-a376-01183711a4a0.text: Will it mean my food will burn less often?

36e54646-b752-4f9f-9ae5-f12dc6c560ef.title: Cook
36e54646-b752-4f9f-9ae5-f12dc6c560ef.text: Well, that's what the salesman told us anyway...
